": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"a city decree\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 347}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision \\\"is linked to a range of free festivities organised by the city, away from the sports venues\\\" and is justified \\\"by the exceptional nature of the opening and closing ceremonies,\\\" the ruling from the city prefect says.\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 363}, {\"ngram\": \"a range\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"free festivities\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 405}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 427}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports venues\", \"from\": 439, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"the exceptional nature\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening and closing ceremonies\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"the ruling\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 552}, {\"ngram\": \"the city prefect\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It means bars will be able to stay open all night on 26 July, when theOlympicsare set to open with a boat parade on the river Seine, as well as the closing ceremony on 11 August.\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 760, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bars\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 595}, {\"ngram\": \"26 July\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 642}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsare\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"a boat parade\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 694}, {\"ngram\": \"the river Seine\", \"from\": 698, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"the closing ceremony\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"11 August\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ALSO READ:Simbine, Rooskrantz announced as Team SA's Olympic flag bearers The same exception to licensing rules will be made for the opening of the Paralympic Games on 28 August and the closing ceremony on 8 September.\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 810, \"e